  "title": "Technical Sales Engineer (Electrical / Industrial) #77201",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: MNC Industrial Electrical Technical Solutions Provider</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Technical Sales Engineer</strong></li><li>Working Location: Central – Toa Payoh</li><li>Working Hours: 5 days / Monday to Friday: 8.30 am-5.30 pm</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Up to SGD 4500 + Performance Bonus</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Analyze clients’ technical requirements and recommend tailored solutions</li><li>Craft and deliver engaging technical presentations, product demos, and proposals</li><li>Lead pre-sales activities, including site visits, technical inquiries, and tender submissions</li><li>Collaborate with engineering and product teams to develop customized applications and support</li><li>Provide post-sales technical assistance and conduct training sessions as needed</li><li>Oversee major accounts including international conglomerates, government bodies, and top consulting firms</li><li>Support regional branches in business development and marketing initiatives</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma in Electrical/Mechatronics/Electronic/Mechanical Engineering</li><li>Min. 1 year of working experience in related field</li><li>Experience in power systems, UPS, or related sectors is a plus</li><li>Training is provided to inexperience candidate</li><li>Ability to read and interpret technical drawings, specifications, and schematics</li><li>Proficiency in Microsoft Office, AutoCAD, or other relevant engineering software is an advantage</li><li>Willingness to travel for client meetings and site visits</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#77201 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Angel Lim | EA Reg No.: R1769781</p>",
